  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>Casual Southern California charm resembling private beachside residences, JW Marriott Santa Monica Le Merigot provides guests with an informal yet elegant retreat that is unrivaled by other hotels in Santa Monica, California. Room furnishings include down duvets and feather pillows, plush chairs and stunning marble baths. Enjoy thoughtful concierge services and access to private pool, excellent meeting suites and scenic beach promenades hotel in Santa Monica. Only a short walk from luxurious suites is Le Merigot's full-service European-style spa and award-winning restaurant, every need will be graciously met. Hotel also allows pets for an additional charge, contact hotel for more information.
 

Facility Includes :
- Valet parking $35 (fee subject to change)
- Wireless Internet access $14.95 Complimentary for Platinum and Gold Marriot members (fee subject to change)
- Hair dryer
- Iron/Ironing board
- Clock radio
- In-room safe
- Complimentary newspapers in lobby
- Multi-line phone
- Voicemail
- Business services
- Video-game console
- Restaurant(s) in hotel
- Complementary Fitness Center 
- Spa services on site
- Outdoor swimming pool&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</Text>
